TITLE: Fetch Single Record with useGetOne
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to fetch a single user record using the `useGetOne` hook from react-admin. It handles loading and error states, and displays user details upon successful data retrieval.

SOURCE: https://github.com/marmelab/react-admin/blob/master/docs/DataFetchingGuide.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
